				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$\backsimeq$$\end{document}TL) or nanoscale vacuum transistors8 where phonon-emission process is eliminated. For electrons in the strong nonequilibrium conditions (Te≫\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
				\usepackage{amssymb}
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
